1221.name: E NiCro A (Incoweld A)
1221.Applications: Nicro A Welding Electrode is used for shielded-metal-arc welding of INCOLOY alloys 800 and 800HT, INCONEL alloys 600 and 601, and nickel steels.
1221.Suitable_For:
Nicro A electrodes are used for welding Incoloy alloys 800 and 800HT, Inconel 600 and 601 and Nickel steels. Examples are combinations of stainless steels, carbon steels, INCONEL alloys, INCOLOY alloys, MONEL alloys, and copper-nickel alloys. Because of its versatility, Nicro A Welding Electrode is especially useful for general maintenance welding of equipment exposed to strenuous service conditions.
